<div class="summary">
  <div class="row">
    <div class="badge">Executive Summary ✅</div>
    <div style="flex:1;">
      Paid search visitors are high-intent — but the current landing experience is not guiding them into a fast action path.
      The highest ROI improvements are <b>mobile sticky CTA</b> and <b>full conversion tracking</b>.
      These changes typically lift lead volume and reduce wasted clicks.
      <div class="kpi-grid">
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="label">CRO Readiness Score</div>
          <div class="value">87 / 100</div>
          <div class="progress"><span></span></div>
          <div class="note">Strong foundation — needs CTA + tracking tightening.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="label">Highest Impact Fix</div>
          <div class="value">Mobile CTA</div>
          <div class="note">Add sticky Call / WhatsApp on mobile for Saudi users.</div>
        </div>
        <div class="kpi">
          <div class="label">Measurement Risk</div>
          <div class="value">High</div>
          <div class="note">Calls + WhatsApp attribution must be fully tracked.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<!-- ✅ ADD-ON END -->

<div class="breakdown">
  <h3>Audit Breakdown</h3>

  <div class="step">
    <strong>One</strong>
    Above-the-fold section prioritizes branding instead of immediate lead capture,
    increasing drop-off risk from paid search traffic.
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <strong>Two</strong>
    No sticky mobile Call or WhatsApp CTA, limiting direct enquiry options
    for high-intent Saudi users.
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <strong>Three</strong>
    Payment plan, starting price, and delivery timeline are not clearly visible
    at first interaction.
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <strong>Four</strong>
    reCAPTCHA and single-step form may reduce mobile completion rate.
  </div>

  <div class="step">
    <strong>Five</strong>
    Call and WhatsApp actions may not be fully tracked in Google Ads.
  </div>
</div>

<h3>Priority Findings & Severity</h3>

<table>
<tr>
<th>Category</th>
<th>Status</th>
<th>Impact</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Mobile CTA Optimization</td>
<td><span class="pill critical">Critical</span></td>
<td>Absence of sticky contact reduces qualified enquiries.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Above-the-Fold Conversion</td>
<td><span class="pill warning">Warning</span></td>
<td>Brand-first layout reduces paid traffic efficiency.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Financial Visibility</td>
<td><span class="pill warning">Warning</span></td>
<td>Lack of price clarity may increase hesitation.</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Conversion Tracking</td>
<td><span class="pill critical">Critical</span></td>
<td>Incomplete attribution limits ROI optimization.</td>
</tr>
</table>

<!-- ✅ ADD-ON START (Next Steps) -->
