    <li><b>7 Days (Quick Wins)</b> <span class="mini">High ROI</span> — Add sticky mobile Call/WhatsApp CTA + shorten form friction (test removing extra fields).</li>
    <li><b>14 Days (Conversion Clarity)</b> <span class="mini">Reduce drop-off</span> — Make price range, payment plan, and delivery timeline visible above-the-fold.</li>
    <li><b>30 Days (Measurement & Optimization)</b> <span class="mini">Smart bidding</span> — Track calls + WhatsApp properly (Google Ads conversions + GA4 events) to enable accurate ROI optimization.</li>
  </ul>
